name: Myreact
tagline: My first react redux thingy. It felt good while making it work. It has least possible content for easy understanding, and a kind of boilerplate to move things here and there and start from it.
body:
### MyReact
This is my implementation of React.js. I wanted to do this, because I learned how to do it, and I figured I could help someone learn React and Redux in a best possible way I could, though I am a beginner.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
